Package: KnitFmt
Type: Package
Title: Formatting HTML and PDF of rmarkdown documents
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sébastien Rochette
Maintainer: Sébastien Rochette <sebastienrochettefr@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions to be used in rmarkdown documents
    to allow text formatting for both HTML and PDF. A tutorial is here: 
    https://statnmap.com/wp-content/uploads/rmarkdown/Rmd_tips_EN.html
